node.title: Man hospitalised after being shot in west Auckland
node.description: A man is in hospital in a stable condition after being shot in Henderson, west Auckland.
node.content: ["A man is in hospital in a stable condition after being shot in Henderson, west Auckland.", "Police officers were called to a Woodford Avenue property early this morning and found the man with a gunshot injury.", "It is yet to be established what was behind the shooting."]
